description: Looking for something random to do in Austin? Have an Echo? Well now is your chance to ask for a random happy hour or event around town, simply by asking Dillo to dig it up. You can either ask for a random happy hour or event happening tonight, or ask according to day of the week Monday through Sunday.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Dillo to dig me up a happy hour.
Alexa, ask Dillo to dig me up a happy hour on Sunday.
Alexa, ask Dillo to get me a show.
name: ATX Dillo
shortDescription: The Dillo will dig you up a happy hour or event around Austin, either tonight or a day within the next week.
